Hallee Hirsh https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hallee_Hirsh 0 Hallee Leah Hirsh (born December 16, 1987) is an American actress known for her roles as Mattie on JAG, Daley in the children's series Flight 29 Down, and as the adolescent and young adult Rachel Greene on ER. Starring alongside Kristen Stewart, Hirsh played Rachel Bruin in Speak.
